name: The Erin Tote Bag
description: This beautiful color combo will be great all year round. Measuring 12.5"Wx10.5"Hx3.5"D, it is roomy enough to fit it all but not to huge to hurt your back! Lined in a soft blue silk with decorative stitching to accent the color blocking.

name: The Cassandra Bag
description:
A roomy bag to carry it all! Measures 11"Hx14"Wx6"D. Outer Fabric is a gorgeous Eddie Bauer floral of cranberry and cream. The lining fabric is a Sharon Yentor cotton paisley with hints of cranberry, green and blue on a cream background.

The strap is 20" long and can be worn on the shoulder or across the chest. Toggle button and loop closure.

Makes a beautiful bag for the holidays, as a gift, and could even be used as a small overnight bag.

name: The Kate Bag
description:
Reminiscent of the 1950's when bows were a strong element in fashion, this wool tweed bag will really make a statement!

Approximately 7" deep by 10" wide exclusing the handle. The details on this are what make this bag truly one of a kind. The wool tweed in tan and brown check, the burnout velvet on the handle, and the silk lining all compliment each other to create a stunning design. Magnetic closure

name: The Evelyn Bag
description:
I love how this turned out!! This elegant evening bag is made from a beautiful tapestry fabric in browns, golds, and rusts. Measuring only 6.5"W at base and 1.5"D x 5" H (excluding handle), this perfect little purse is just the right size for that fabulous evening out.

The bag is lined with a tufted taffeta material that adds to the total effect. Embellished with a vintage shoe pendant and taffeta rosette.
